thread.title: Pamela

author: Pamela
title: Pamela
text: Before you try any other travel or flight websites. You should definitely check Flight Hub first. Out of all the websites that I viewed they really honestly have the cheapest rate you need to check all your go to websites and compare ticket prices first before you book any tickets. I'm postive you will not find a cheaper rate. I compare their rate for $372 to all the rest of sites and the same ticket was over $600.
